<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center; font-size:larger; background-color:#6495ED; color:#000000;" class="fn summary"><b>Damien Hirst</b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center; font-size:90%;" class=""><a href="/wiki/File:Damien-Hirst-1.jpg" class="image" title="Damien-Hirst-1.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ad/Damien-Hirst-1.jpg/220px-Damien-Hirst-1.jpg" width="220" height="287" border="0" /></a><br />
<small>Damien Hirst</small></td>
</tr>
